'#minify()'
'should leave <pre> alone'

'to minify to'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><pre>  foo bar  </pre></body></html>'
'should leave SSI comment alone'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><!--#echo "foo"--></body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><!--#echo "foo"--></body></html>'
'should preserve Knockout containerless binding comment, but remove its leading and trailing whitespace'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><!-- ko foreach: blah --><div></div><!--/ko --></body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><!--ko foreach: blah--><div></div><!--/ko--></body></html>'
'should preserve an already minified Knockout containerless binding comment'
'should preserve Htmlizer containerless binding comment, but remove its leading and trailing whitespace'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><!-- hz foreach: blah --><div></div><!--/hz --></body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><!--hz foreach: blah--><div></div><!--/hz--></body></html>'
'should remove leading whitespace in the first text node child of a block-level element'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>   blah</div></body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah</div></body></html>'
'should remove leading whitespace in the first text node child of a block-level element with comment in the middle'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div> <!--foo-->  blah</div></body></html>'
'should remove different types of leading whitespace in the first text node child of a block-level element'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>\t   \nblah</div></body></html>'
'should remove trailing whitespace in the last text node child of a block-level element'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah   </div></body></html>'
'should remove trailing whitespace in the last text node child of a block-level element with comment in the middle'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah <!--foo-->  </div></body></html>'
'should remove different types of trailing whitespace in last text node child of a block-level element'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah   \n\t</div></body></html>'
'should compress sequences of more than one whitespace char in text nodes'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah   blah</div></body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah blah</div></body></html>'
'should compress sequences of different types of whitespace char in text nodes'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>blah \n\t  blah</div></body></html>'
'should remove an all-whitespace text node'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div>   </div></body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div></div></body></html>'
'should remove an all-whitespace text node between block-level elements'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body>    <div></div></body></html>'
'should remove leading and trailing whitespace between block-level'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html>   <head> \r\n   </head> \n\n <body>    <div>    </div>    </body>    </html>'
'should leave a text node consisting of a single non-breaking space alone'

'should compress whitespace before and after <span data-i18n="..."> should be compressed down to one'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body>  Here is the thing:  <span data-i18n="blah">foo</span>  and furthermore...  </body></html>'
'<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body>Here is the thing: <span data-i18n=blah>foo</span> and furthermore...</body></html>'
'should keep one leading/trailing space in text nodes below elements with data-i18n'
'<div><span data-i18n="ShowingXToYOfZ">\n    <span>1</span>\n     -                <span>50</span>\nof                      <span>0</span>\n            </span>\n</div>'
'<div><span data-i18n=ShowingXToYOfZ><span>1</span> - <span>50</span> of <span>0</span></span></div>'

describe
"replaceSyncBlock"
"case 1 (Task)"
"t = Task ->"
"  a = 100"
"  b = [ 1, 2, 3 ].map (x)->"
"    a * x"
"t = Task syncblock ->"
"  a = b = undefined"
"  ["
"    ->"
"      a = 100"
"      b = [ 1, 2, 3 ].map (x)->"
"        a * x"
"  ]"
replaceSyncBlock
"case 2 (num.do)"
"s = Synth()"
"[ 1, 2, 3 ].do syncblock (i)->"
"  s.set freq:(60+i).midicps()"
"  0.1.wait()"
"[ 1, 2, 3 ].do syncblock ->"
"    (i)->"
"      s.set freq:(60+i).midicps()"
"      0.1.wait()"
"case 3 (nesting)"
"t = Task ->"
"  a = 100"
"  1.wait()"
"  s = Synth('test').on 'end', ->"
"    s.stop()"
"  [ 1, 2, 3 ].do syncblock (i)->"
"    s.set freq:(60+i).midicps()"
"    0.1.wait()"
"t.start()"
"t = Task syncblock ->"
"  a = s = undefined"
"    ->"
"      a = 100"
"      1.wait()"
"    ->"
"      s = Synth('test').on 'end', ->"
"        s.stop()"
"      [ 1, 2, 3 ].do syncblock ->"
"        ["
"          (i)->"
"            s.set freq:(60+i).midicps()"
"            0.1.wait()"
"        ]"
"case 4 (if)"
"Task ->"
"  a = b = c = false"
"  if a"
"  else if b"
"    0.2.wait()"
"  else"
"    if c"
"      console.log c"
"      0.3.wait()"
"Task syncblock ->"
"  a = b = c = undefined"
"      a = b = c = false"
"      if a"
"        0.1.wait()"
"      else if b"
"        0.2.wait()"
"      else"
"        if c"
"          console.log c"
"          0.3.wait()"
"case 5 (if syncblock)"
"  if a then syncblock ->"
"  else if b then syncblock ->"
"  else syncblock ->"
"    if c then syncblock ->"
"        syncblock ->"
"          ["
"            -> 0.1.wait()"
"          ]"
"        syncblock ->"
"          ["
"            -> 0.2.wait()"
"          ]"
"        syncblock ->"
"          ["
"            -> if c"
"              syncblock ->"
"                ["
"                  ->"
"                    console.log c"
"                    0.3.wait()"
"                ]"
"          ]"
"case 6 (assign)"
"10.do syncblock ([a, b, c], d)->"
"  console.log a"
"  1.wait()"
"10.do syncblock ->"
"    ([a, b, c], d)->"
"      console.log a"
"      1.wait()"
"case 7"
"(out)->"
"  syncblock (i)->"
"    a = out * i"
"  syncblock ->"
"    a = undefined"
"    ["
"      (i)-> a = out * i"
"    ]"

"test"
SynthDef
"$a = SynthDef \"synth\", (amp=0.5, trig)->"
"  freq = [ +\"A4\", -\"A4\" ].midicps() *S* [ 1, 1.005 ]"
"  SinOsc.ar(freq) * Line.kr(\"1min\", 0, amp)"
"syncblock (i, j)->"
"  i += ~0"
"  i.wait()"
"  if j then syncblock ->"
"    10.wait()"
"  if true"
"    x = 0"
"((global, cc)->"
"  global.a = cc.SynthDef(\"synth\", (amp, trig)->"
"    freq = [ 69.__plus__(), 69.__minus__() ].midicps().__mul__([ 1, 1.005 ], SHORT)"
"    SinOsc.ar(freq).__mul__(Line.kr(60, 0, amp))"
"  , [ 'amp', '0.5', 'trig', '0' ])"
"  syncblock ->"
"    x = undefined"
"    ["
"      (i, j)->"
"        i = i.__add__(~0)"
"        i.wait()"

"        if j then syncblock ->"

"            -> 10.wait()"
"          ]"

"        if true"

").call(cc.__context__, this.self || global, cc)"
